oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22590-4
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Feel: always striving to play fairly and follow the rules of the game shows
  integrity."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.277963Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22590-5
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Connect: in game situations we must communicate effectively so our team understands
  the tactics we are applying."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.277967Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22349-1
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Move: marking successfully requires us to follow the movements of the attacker and
  stay close without making contact."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.277971Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22349-2
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Move: staying close to an attacker and reacting to their movements increases a
  defender’s chances of forcing an error."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.277974Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22349-3
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Think: concentrating on the movements of the attacker and staying close helps us
  mark effectively and force an error."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.277978Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22349-4
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Feel: continuing to follow the attacker as we mark them leads to success and shows
  the self motivation to succeed."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.277982Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22349-5
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Connect: respecting the player we are marking and not making contact demonstrates a
  commitment to playing by the rules."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.277985Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22421-1
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Move: marking involves being close to the attacker and staying positioned between
  the player and the ball."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.278008Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22421-2
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Move: defending well requires us to mark opponents by standing tall with arms ready
  to move up or out to stop a pass."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.278012Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22421-3
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Think: it’s important to evaluate and improve our marking technique to reduce
  scoring opportunities for our opponents."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.278015Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22421-4
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Feel: when trying to defend and win the ball back, it is important to play within
  the rules and show self-discipline."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.278019Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22421-5
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Connect: taking responsibility to ensure all our teammates are marking an opponent
  demonstrates excellent leadership."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.278023Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22419-1
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Move: dribbling the ball with control and changing direction helps us beat a
  defender and creates scoring chances."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.278043Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22419-2
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Think: selecting between bounce or chest passes helps outwit our opponents, creating
  scoring opportunities."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.278047Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22419-3
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Think: quick decisions as to whether to pass or dribble in a game situation
  increases our chance of keeping possession."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.278051Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22419-4
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Feel: encouraging our teammates, even when they make mistakes, shows that we are an
