  intake and improve endurance."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.280568Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22462-3
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Think: pacing ourselves in a long distance race is a good tactic to allow us to
  reserve energy for a sprint finish."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.280572Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22462-4
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Feel: applying running tactics and completing the run without stopping shows
  determination."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.280576Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22462-5
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Connect: communicating and discussing race tactics helps us to improve our
  performance."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.280580Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22403-1
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Move: when throwing for distance, stand sideways on, arm up, elbow bent, releasing
  the bean bag just past your head."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.282472Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22403-2
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Move: when throwing underarm for accuracy, step into your throw and aim towards the
  target."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.282479Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22403-3
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Think: if we release the beanbag too late it will go towards the floor but if we
  release too early it will go too high."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.282483Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-22403-4
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Feel: focus on remaining positive and determined even when we are finding throwing
